data.description: As soon as you walk in, you can feel the potential of this home. Hardwood floors thru-out most of the home. 4 Bedrooms 2.5 Baths with a basement. Nice Laundry room, covered deck, and a storage across a walkable bridge. Whole House water filter installed and at the sink. Home needs some tlc, and you will still love this home.
